    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of life left? This car is a solid choice! It has some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, but it remains a dependable and functional vehicle that gets the job done. While it shows its age in a few spots, it's a great opportunity to own a quality ride at a very accessible price point!",
