      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting zero wear and a flawless mechanical profile. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine specimen. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, ensuring an uncompromising driving experience. Inspection by appointment is highly recommended.",
