    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve been so meticulous with it\u2014there's not a single blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone new to take it out on the road. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Come swing by and take a look, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
